author: jacopoc
msg: Fixed bug reported by Giorgio Tomaselli: when the same order item requiring production runs is associated to multiple shipments, in the "work with shipment plans" screen it was not possible to generate the production runs for 2nd, 3rd etc.. shipments.
Fixed by adding an optional shipGroupSeqId to the WorkOrderItemFulfillment entity that can be used to specify the key to the specific OrderItemShipGroupAssoc.
